OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1781867966
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'remarkable'
OL,4,Cpolice officer who died in the line of
OL,5,Cduty
OL,7,FThe parents of a Northumbria Police
OL,8,Fofficer who died in the line of duty
OL,9,Fhave paid tribute to her, describing
OL,10,Fher as "remarkable" and saying she was
OL,11,Ftheir "greatest pride and greatest
OL,12,Fjoy".
OL,14,FPC Jess Turnbull was responding to a
OL,15,Fcollision in Cramlington on the night
OL,16,Fof Monday 8 June, when she was hit by
OL,17,Fa car unconnected to the original
OL,18,Fincident.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1781867966
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'remarkable'
OL,4,Cpolice officer who died in the line of
OL,5,Cduty
OL,7,FJess was taken to hospital for
OL,8,Ftreatment for her injuries, but died
OL,9,Fon Wednesday surrounded by her loved
OL,10,Fones.
OL,12,FOn Monday (15 June), Jess's parents
OL,13,FJanice and Andy Turnbull released a
OL,14,Ftribute to her, and revealed that Jess
OL,15,Fhad followed in her father's footsteps
OL,16,Fafter he too served with Northumbria
OL,17,FPolice.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1781867966
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'remarkable'
OL,4,Cpolice officer who died in the line of
OL,5,Cduty
OL,7,FThey have said they are "utterly
OL,8,Fdevastated", adding that the loss of
OL,9,F19-year-old Jess, who was their only
OL,10,Fchild, leaves a hole in their lives
OL,11,Fthat is impossible to put into words.
OL,13,FJanice and Andy went on to share
OL,14,Fstories of Jess's interests and
OL,15,Fpassions, saying: "From a young age,
OL,16,FJess was full of energy,
OL,17,Fdetermination, and kindness. She loved
OL,18,Fsport and spent much of her childhood
OL,19,Fplaying football and competing as a
OL,20,Fswimmer.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1781867966
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'remarkable'
OL,4,Cpolice officer who died in the line of
OL,5,Cduty
OL,7,F"Her passion for helping others was
OL,8,Fevident even then and she later
OL,9,Fvolunteered her time coaching young
OL,10,Fchildren in football, encouraging them
OL,11,Fto believe in themselves and enjoy the
OL,12,Fgame she loved so much.
OL,14,F"Jess recently found happiness with
OL,15,Fher boyfriend Dan. They had been
OL,16,Ftogether for a year and were
OL,17,Finseparable.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1781867966
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'remarkable'
OL,4,Cpolice officer who died in the line of
OL,5,Cduty
OL,7,F"One of Jess' proudest achievements
OL,8,Fwas becoming a police officer. She
OL,9,Fabsolutely loved serving her community
OL,10,Fand was incredibly proud to wear the
OL,11,Funiform. Following in the footsteps of
OL,12,Fher dad, Andy, was something she had
OL,13,Falways dreamed of doing, and seeing
OL,14,Fher achieve that ambition filled us
OL,15,Fboth with immense pride.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1781867966
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'remarkable'
OL,4,Cpolice officer who died in the line of
OL,5,Cduty
OL,7,F"Jess touched the lives of so many
OL,8,Fpeople during her short life. She was
OL,9,Fcaring, funny, determined, and
OL,10,Ffiercely loyal to those she loved. She
OL,11,Fhad an infectious smile and a way of
OL,12,Fmaking everyone feel valued and
OL,13,Fwelcome.
OL,15,F"While our hearts are broken, we are
OL,16,Fincredibly proud of the remarkable
OL,17,Fyoung woman Jess became. We will miss
OL,18,Fher every single day, but we will
OL,19,Fcarry her love, her spirit, and our
OL,20,Fmemories of her with us forever.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1781867966
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'remarkable'
OL,4,Cpolice officer who died in the line of
OL,5,Cduty
OL,7,F"We would like to thank everyone for
OL,8,Fthe overwhelming kindness, support,
OL,9,Fand condolences we have received
OL,10,Fduring this unimaginably difficult
OL,11,Ftime. Knowing how much Jess was loved
OL,12,Fand respected has brought us comfort.
OL,14,F"Jess was, and always will be, our
OL,15,Fgreatest pride and our greatest joy."
OL,17,FMeanwhile, Northumbria Police are
OL,18,Fcontinuing to investigate the
OL,19,Fcollision which led to Jess's death,
OL,20,Fand are urging anyone with information
OL,21,Fto contact them.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
